    Megatron looked to Quickstrike. He hated the little worm. Ever scince he 
joined with Aracnia he had changed. The loyal little expendable soldier he 
once knew was dead....this new Quickstrike was intelligent. And a soldier 
with intelligence often caused trouble.
    "Its bots like you, roach, that are making the Predacon reunion so 
difficult! I only want to help, you only want to cause trouble. How yo came 
to be Sub-Commander is beyond my comprehension. Yes." Megatron said as he 
looked down from atop rampages shoulders.
    Rampage entered the clearing that contained the ship. He could see 
Inferno, Tarantulas, Aerostreak, Tankkor, Paralysis, and Black Aracnia 
standing waiting for them. Most of them withdrew there guns at the sight of 
Megatron.
    "What do you think your doing?!?!?! That is the traitor!" Inferno yelled, 
going into a fighting stance, his body ridged and flexed.
    Megatron frowned. "Tut tut my fellow commrads....I want to help yo-
    Before he could get another word out, Inferno blasted his head off of his 
body and sent in falling to the ground. Rampage then dropped his body.
    "Take him inside. we can remove his arms and legs...that way he wont hurt 
anything, or anyone. Come on troops, lets move in." Aracnia said ushering in 
her troops. 
    "Anything wrong Quickstuff?" She asked kindly, smileing....for once.
